<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>Alfred Wright</author>
<hymn_number>75</hymn_number>
<title>Chisʋs pi Okchalinchi, pi̱ Mi̱ko ma! ƲIT75</title>
<time_sig>11.11.11.11.</time_sig>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Chisʋs pi Okchalinchi, pi̱ Mi̱ko ma!
 Chisno yoka e chin tahpahanlʋshke;
 Enchil moma kʋt chi holitoblashke,
 Ʋba Mi̱ko ʋt chisno ak banoshke.

[V2]
 Pi Okchalinchi ma! Hina hanta ka
 Pi fohkit ish pi apelahanchashke;
 Chisʋs ma! Chisʋs ma! Chisno ak bano
 Chim antia pi baha̱nna fehnʋshke.

[V3]
 Chi̱ nana ʋlhpisa holitopa ma
 Pi chu̱kʋsh a̱ ish a holissohonchit,
 Nana ish pim ahni kak o̱ ithanʋt,
 E chim antia chi̱, ish pim ahnashke.

[V4]
 Pi okcha̱ya ta̱kla kʋt chiba nowʋt,
 Il itʋnoho̱wa hokbano, ahnit
 Pillikmʋt, ʋba ya̱ ont chiba fohkʋt
 Il anta na bilia, il ahnishke.</lyrics>
</song>